      "title": "Ali Sabri starts work",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Foreign Affairs Mr. Ali Sabri started his duties today (25th) at the Ministry. In the recent cabinet reshuffle, former Minister of Foreign Affairs Prof. G.L. He proceeded to remove Mr. Peiris from that position."
